AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GENEPIO_0001120> "A data specification established for use by The Canadian COVID-19 Genomics Network (CanCOGeN) project for SARS-CoV-2 contextual data (metadata) harmonization and curation across data providers."@en)
