AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasExactSynonym> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GENEPIO_0001120> "The Canadian COVID-19 Genomics Network SARS-CoV-2 specification"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasExactSynonym> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GENEPIO_0001120> "The Canadian COVID-19 Genomics Network severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 specification"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasExactSynonym> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GENEPIO_0001120> "The Canadian coronavirus 2019 Genomics Network severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 specification"@en)
