AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GENEPIO_0100279> "A variant designation which is 1) a variant of the Severe Acute Respiratory Syndrome Coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), 2) containing genetic mutates that may increase binding affinity to human cells, 3) linked to rapid spread in human populations, 4) is being monitored, and 5) denoted as a lower risk than a Variant of Interest (VOI)."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000118> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GENEPIO_0100279> "Variant Under Monitoring (VUM)"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.org/dc/terms/contributor> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GENEPIO_0100279> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1107-9135>)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.org/dc/terms/contributor> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GENEPIO_0100279> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-8844-9165>)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.org/dc/terms/contributor> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GENEPIO_0100279> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-9578-0788>)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.org/dc/terms/date> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GENEPIO_0100279> "2022-01-19T18:23:15.862Z"^^xsd:dateTime)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasExactSynonym> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GENEPIO_0100279> "VBM"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasExactSynonym> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GENEPIO_0100279> "VUM"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasExactSynonym> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GENEPIO_0100279> "Variant Being Monitored"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GENEPIO_0100279> "PHA4GE Definition: A category used for indicating that a variant of the Severe Acute Respiratory Syndrome Coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2) containing genetic mutations that may increase binding affinity to human cells and linked to rapid spread in human populations is being monitored. This category denotes less risk than a Variant of Interest (VOI)."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GENEPIO_0100279> "variant under monitoring (SARS-CoV-2)"@en)
SubClassOf(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GENEPIO_0100279> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GENEPIO_0100293>)

