AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GENEPIO_0100562> "A data item which is a statement confirming that quality control processes were carried out and no quality issues were detected."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000118> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GENEPIO_0100562> "no quality control issues identified"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.org/dc/terms/contributor> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GENEPIO_0100562> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1107-9135>)
